<div class="p-8">
  <h4 class="pb-3">
    <%= Proposal.steps[@proposal.quality_control_step - 1] %>
  </h4>
<label for="check_pin" class="flex items-center space-x-3 pb-3">
    <input id="check_pin" type="checkbox" name="check_pin" value="1" class="form-tick appearance-none h-6 w-6 border border-gray-300 rounded-md checked:bg-blue-600 checked:border-transparent focus:outline-none" required>
    <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Make sure Aurora put the pin on the right house. (Good to check the address in
    Google)</span>
  </label>
  <label for="check_lidar" class="flex items-center space-x-3 pb-3">
    <input id="check_lidar" type="checkbox" name="check_lidar" value="1" class="form-tick appearance-none h-6 w-6 border border-gray-300 rounded-md checked:bg-blue-600 checked:border-transparent focus:outline-none" required>
    <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">&nbsp;Check LIDAR or Google Maps/Earth street view, is the house accurately designed? (Pitch,Height, Obstructions)</span>
  </label>
  <label for="check_panels" class="flex items-center space-x-3 pb-3">
    <input id="check_panels" type="checkbox" name="check_panels" value="1" class="form-tick appearance-none h-6 w-6 border border-gray-300 rounded-md checked:bg-blue-600 checked:border-transparent focus:outline-none" required>
    <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">&nbsp;Look closely at the house, are all the roof faces drawn correctly? If you move the panels out of the way, do you see obstructions that were missed on the roof?</span>
  </label>
</div>

